A medical worker takes a nasal swab sample for nucleic acid testing at the Eighth People's Hospital of Shanghai in east China's Shanghai, Oct. 30, 2021. Shanghai enhanced nucleic acid testing capacity for the upcoming 2021 China International Import Expo (CIIE) as more than 21 medical institutions in the city provide 24-hour uninterrupted nucleic acid testing services from Thursday and the test results will be reported within six hours. (Xinhua/Liu Ying)  